cu_modifications.explanation: Setting max_num_UE to 0, which is below the valid range (minimum 1), will cause UE connection rejection and prevent any UEs from connecting to the gNB.
cu_modifications.explanation_zh: 將 max_num_UE 設定為 0，低於有效範圍 (最小值 1)，會導致 UE 連接被拒絕，並阻止任何 UE 連接到 gNB。

du_modifications.explanation: Setting local_n_portd to 0, which is below the valid port range (1-65535), will cause F1 data interface binding failure and prevent DU-CU communication.
du_modifications.explanation_zh: 將 local_n_portd 設定為 0，低於有效端口範圍 (1-65535)，會導致 F1 數據接口綁定失敗，並阻止 DU-CU 通信。
